2009-03-13  Wim Lavrijsen <WLavrijsen@lbl.gov>
        * inital attempt to run inside a private dict, to improve cleanup
        * improved cleanup code

            Note: this code will block all such codes that do (wrongly):

              from AthenaCommon.AppMgr import AlgSequence
              from __main__ import ToolSvc

            or otherwise touch __main__. The above two should be:

              from AthenaCommon.AlgSequence import AlgSequence
              from AthenaCommon.AppMgr import ToolSvc

